ADDITIONAL NOTICE

This project is a clean-room server emulator and client patcher for the game
"Dying Light: Bad Blood" by Techland S.A.

This project does NOT include, redistribute, or in any way bundle any
proprietary game assets, binaries, or data from Techland. To use this project
you must own a legitimate copy of Dying Light: Bad Blood obtained through
official Steam purchase prior to the game's removal from sale.

"Dying Light: Bad Blood", the Dying Light franchise, and all related assets
are property of Techland S.A. This project is not affiliated with, endorsed
by, or sponsored by Techland.

Third-party tools referenced (Goldberg Steam Emulator, Steamless, QuickBMS,
stunnel, Dear ImGui, FastAPI) are governed by their own licenses. See
docs/credits.md for attribution.

This project exists for game preservation and educational purposes.
